== '''Amateka''' ==
Dr Daniel Ngamiye ni Umunyarwanda utuye mugihugu cy' [[Rwanda]]. akaba ari Minisitiri w' Ubuzima mu [[Rwanda]]. Amashuri ye ya kaminuza yayigiye muri Universite de Kinshasa, DRC yigayo Bachelor's degree in Medicine and Surgery. Yakomereje kandi amashuri ye muri Universite Libre de Bruxelles muri Brussels, Beligum aho yigaga Masters of Medicine in Public Health. Kuva mu mwaka wa 1995 kugeza 1997 Dr Daniel Ngamije yabaye umu dogiteri mubitaro bya Kabgayi.<ref>https://www.gpmb.org/board/item/dr-daniel-m.-ngamije</ref> 

